Repositories
The contents of this file have been split into multiple files in the Repositories directory to improve readability.

https://github.com/William-Robert-Robertson/WildCamera/tree/main/Candidate%20Technologies/Repositories

DTOs (Device Tree Overlays) for the Debix 200a camera, Debix 500a camera and IMX335 image sensor for the i.MX 8 M Plus:
Note that these were written for the Debix Model A SBC so may need to be adjusted for the Debix Model A SoM and Debix Model A SoM I/O board.
https://git.uk.ideasonboard.com/camera/dt-overlays/src/branch/main/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale

https://gitlab.com/ideasonboard/nxp/linux/-/commit/2e3ab4d9815eaca81c236924d3393c7ced345619

Dockerfile for buildroot containing current buildroot dependencies
https://gitlab.com/buildroot.org/buildroot/-/blob/master/support/docker/Dockerfile
Note that the above was written for testing buildroot and so the list of dependencies was used for the Docker container for buildroot for WildCamera but not other parts of the above file.

Instructions to generate a Linux image for Debix Model A using Buildroot:
https://github.com/buildroot/buildroot/blob/master/board/polyhex/debix-model-a/readme.txt

buildroot default configuration for Debix Model A SBC
https://github.com/buildroot/buildroot/blob/master/configs/polyhex_debix_model_a_defconfig

buildroot build for Debix Model A SBC
https://github.com/buildroot/buildroot/tree/master/board/polyhex/debix-model-a

